Date: 1996-09-09

Title: Small Instantons, del Pezzo Surfaces and Type I' theory

Authors: M.R. Douglas, S. Katz and C. Vafa

Comments: 21 pages, minor changes

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys. B497 (1997) 155-172

Samll instantons of exceptional groups arise geometrically by a collapsingdel Pezzo surface in a CY. We use this to explain the physics of a 4-braneprobe in Type I' compactification to 9 dimensions.